thread.title: BRIEF-Inca One Gold Reports Feb Production Of 2,018 Tonnes Of Material

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Inca One Gold Reports Feb Production Of 2,018 Tonnes Of Material
text:
March 6 (Reuters) - Inca One Gold Corp:
* INCA ONE GOLD REPORTS RECORD PROCESSING FOR THE MONTH OF FEBRUARY
* INCA ONE GOLD - PRODUCTION IN FEB REACHED 2,018 TONNES OF MATERIAL OR 72 TONNES PER DAY, UP FROM 1,522 TONNES OR 49 TPD PROCESSED IN 2017
* INCA ONE GOLD CORP - GOLD EXPORTS IN FEBRUARY 2018 REACHED OVER 910 OUNCES, COMPARED TO 2017 PRODUCTION OF 624 OUNCES OF GOLD Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
